WEBVTT

00:04.535 --> 00:06.207
HE'S DEAD.

00:06.207 --> 00:07.408
I DIDN'T HAVE A CHOICE.

00:07.408 --> 00:09.410
HE SHOT AT ME.
I HAD TO RETURN FIRE.

00:09.410 --> 00:10.711
KATE, YOU'RE HIT.

00:10.711 --> 00:14.115
NO, NO. I'M FINE.
I-I HAVE MY VEST ON.

00:15.716 --> 00:17.588
WHERE IS SHE?
WHO?

00:17.588 --> 00:19.790
THE WOMAN
WHO RICKFORD WAS RAPING.

00:19.790 --> 00:21.152
WHERE IS SHE?

00:21.152 --> 00:24.155
I DON'T...

00:24.155 --> 00:26.297
THERE'S SOME STAIRS HERE.
MAYBE SHE RAN DOWN.

00:26.297 --> 00:29.200
LET'S GET SOME AIR.
COME ON.

00:31.532 --> 00:34.705
JUST --
JUST TAKE A DEEP BREATH.

00:34.705 --> 00:37.068
CPD IS ON THE WAY.

00:37.068 --> 00:39.110
911 ALREADY GOT
FOUR CALLS.

00:39.110 --> 00:41.812
WELL, WHAT THEY HELL ARE THE TWO
OF YOU DOING HERE ANYWAY?

00:41.812 --> 00:44.215
WE HADN'T HEARD FROM YOU, KATE.
WE WERE WORRIED.

00:44.215 --> 00:46.347
THE QUESTION IS
WHY ARE YOU HERE?

00:46.347 --> 00:49.180
I'VE BEEN FOLLOWING RICKFORD
FOR THE PAST FEW DAYS.
JESUS, KATE

00:49.180 --> 00:52.323
THEY ALREADY TOOK YOUR GUN AND
BADGE FOR HARASSING THIS GUY.

00:52.323 --> 00:55.186
WELL, I COULDN'T
JUST LET IT GO.

00:55.186 --> 00:57.528
I KNEW THAT SOONER OR LATER HE
WAS GONNA ATTACK ANOTHER WOMAN,

00:57.528 --> 00:59.230
AND I WAS RIGHT.

00:59.230 --> 01:01.662
TONIGHT HE WENT TO A BAR.
HE WAS HITTING ON THIS GIRL.

01:01.662 --> 01:03.664
I SAW HIM.

01:03.664 --> 01:06.797
HE SLIPPED SOMETHING
INTO HER DRINK.

01:09.270 --> 01:11.272
SHE DIDN'T WANT TO
GET INTO HIS CAR,

01:11.272 --> 01:13.774
BUT SHE WAS --
SHE WAS TOO WASTED TO RESIST.

01:13.774 --> 01:15.706
SO I FOLLOWED THEM HERE.

01:20.811 --> 01:24.355
I SAW HIM THROUGH THE WINDOW.
HE WAS GETTING ROUGH WITH HER.

01:24.355 --> 01:25.816
[ SCREAMS ]

01:25.816 --> 01:27.858
SHE SCREAMED.
I HAD TO GO IN THERE.

01:32.193 --> 01:34.525
FBI!

01:43.304 --> 01:45.706
BUT IT WAS LIKE
HE WAS READY FOR ME.

01:58.619 --> 02:01.752
IT WAS A CLEAN SHOOT.
OKAY, I GET THAT.

02:01.752 --> 02:05.726
BUT YOU'RE GONNA HAVE
A LOT OF EXPLAINING TO DO.

02:05.726 --> 02:07.728
YEAH, LIKE WHY YOU
WERE FOLLOWING HIM
IN THE FIRST PLACE.

02:07.728 --> 02:09.460
AND WHY YOU'RE WEARING
BODY ARMOR.

02:09.460 --> 02:11.332
HE'S A TRAINED SOLDIER,
AND I DON'T HAVE ANY BACKUP.

02:11.332 --> 02:13.264
YOU'RE DAMN RIGHT
I'M WEARING A VEST.

02:13.264 --> 02:16.467
[ SIRENS WAILING ]

02:16.467 --> 02:19.440
AS SOON AS WE FIND THAT WOMAN,
SHE'S GONNA CONFIRM MY STORY.

02:25.145 --> 02:28.649
IN THE MEANTIME,
YOU'RE GONNA NEED A LAWYER.

02:34.785 --> 02:37.788
KATIE.
HONEY, YOU OKAY?

02:37.788 --> 02:38.789
I'M FINE, DAD.

02:41.161 --> 02:43.334
WHAT HAPPENS NOW?

02:43.334 --> 02:45.536
WELL, THEY, UH --
THEY INVESTIGATE,

02:45.536 --> 02:47.868
TRY TO FIND THE EYEWITNESS,
I GO TO THERAPY.

02:47.868 --> 02:49.300
STANDARD
OPERATING PROCEDURE

02:49.300 --> 02:50.871
AFTER AN OFFICER-INVOLVED
SHOOTING.

02:50.871 --> 02:52.673
Joe: YEAH,
IT'S A WASTE OF TIME.

02:52.673 --> 02:55.546
NEVER MET A CPD HEADSHRINKER
WHO KNEW HIS ASS FROM HIS ELBOW.

02:55.546 --> 02:58.509
THERAPY CAN BE VERY EFFECTIVE
AFTER A TRAUMATIC EVENT.

02:58.509 --> 03:01.352
I'M NOT TRAUMATIZED.
I'M FINE.

03:01.352 --> 03:02.783
DON'T WORRY ABOUT IT,
KIDDO.

03:02.783 --> 03:06.417
EVERYTHING'S GONNA BE OKAY.

03:08.459 --> 03:11.622
LET ME GUESS --
YOU DON'T NEED TREATMENT?

03:11.622 --> 03:13.494
YEAH, WHAT I NEED
IS TO GET BACK TO WORK,

03:13.494 --> 03:15.195
SO IF YOU COULD
JUST SIGN THE FORMS

03:15.195 --> 03:17.368
SAYING THAT I AM FIT FOR DUTY,
THAT'D BE GREAT.

03:17.368 --> 03:19.930
AS I UNDERSTAND IT, YOU DON'T
HAVE A JOB TO GET BACK TO.

03:19.930 --> 03:22.403
SO YOU'RE NOT
GONNA SIGN IT?

03:22.403 --> 03:24.775
YOU'RE WELCOME TO
STARE AT THE WALLS

03:24.775 --> 03:26.477
FOR THE NEXT 45 MINUTES.

03:26.477 --> 03:28.439
I'VE GOT E-MAILS
TO ANSWER.

03:28.439 --> 03:31.211
BUT THAT WON'T GET YOU
YOUR GUN AND BADGE BACK.

03:31.211 --> 03:33.584
OKAY.
WHAT DO YOU WANT ME TO SAY?

03:33.584 --> 03:36.387
YOU KILLED A MAN.
HOW DOES THAT MAKE YOU FEEL?

03:36.387 --> 03:39.550
WELL, I KILLED
A RAPIST AND A MURDERER.

03:41.392 --> 03:42.493
I FEEL GREAT.

03:42.493 --> 03:44.425
Paul:
I HEARD THE NEWS ABOUT KATE.

03:44.425 --> 03:45.926
HOW IS SHE HOLDING UP?
OH, HOW DO YOU THINK?

03:45.926 --> 03:47.598
I MEAN, SHE --
SHE ALMOST GOT KILLED,

03:47.598 --> 03:49.760
AND NOW THE FBI GESTAPO
IS TREATING HER LIKE A CRIMINAL.

03:49.760 --> 03:51.432
AND INSTEAD OF BEING THERE
FOR HER,

03:51.432 --> 03:53.604
I'VE GOT TO SPOON-FEED NEURO 101
TO A BUNCH OF FRESHMEN.

03:53.604 --> 03:55.466
LOOK, DANIEL, I KNOW
HOW MUCH KATE MEANS TO YOU

03:55.466 --> 03:57.338
AND I KNOW THAT SHE COULD USE
YOUR HELP RIGHT NOW,

03:57.338 --> 04:00.511
SO WHATEVER TIME YOU NEED,
YOU JUST TAKE IT.

04:00.511 --> 04:02.513
THANKS, PAUL.
YEAH.

04:02.513 --> 04:05.376
IN THE MEANTIME, HOW'S IT GOING
WITH THE LOVELY MIRANDA?

04:05.376 --> 04:06.417
[ SCOFFS ] IT ISN'T.

04:06.417 --> 04:07.918
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?
OH, COME ON.

04:07.918 --> 04:11.282
Y-Y-YOU CAN'T JUST REKINDLE
A DECADES-OLD ROMANCE.

04:11.282 --> 04:12.723
WHOA,
WAIT A MINUTE HERE.

04:12.723 --> 04:15.586
I DON'T KNOW WHAT THIS IS ABOUT,
BUT DON'T BE AN IDIOT.

04:15.586 --> 04:18.729
MOST OF US NEVER GET A SECOND
CHANCE WITH OUR FIRST LOVE.

04:22.533 --> 04:23.694
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

04:23.694 --> 04:25.466
DONNIE RYAN?
YEAH.

04:25.466 --> 04:27.468
JUST WANTED TO INTRODUCE MYSELF.
TODD ERLICH.

04:27.468 --> 04:29.340
I'M AN A.U.S.A.
FROM THE NEW YORK OFFICE.

04:29.340 --> 04:30.801
YOU'RE HANDLING
THE INVESTIGATION

04:30.801 --> 04:32.503
INTO KATE'S SHOOTING.

04:32.503 --> 04:35.045
THEY WANTED AN OUTSIDER --
AVOID ANY CONFLICT OF INTEREST.

04:35.045 --> 04:37.908
SURE. THEY GOT YOU HERE
AWFUL FAST.

04:37.908 --> 04:40.381
CONGRESSMAN RICKFORD
MUST HAVE PULLED SOME STRINGS.

04:40.381 --> 04:41.552
HE WON'T INFLUENCE
MY FINDINGS.

04:41.552 --> 04:42.913
AGENT MORETTI WILL GET
A FAIR SHAKE.

04:42.913 --> 04:45.616
HELL, I'M GLAD THIS IS BEING
FAST-TRACKED.

04:45.616 --> 04:47.418
THE SOONER SHE'S CLEARED,
THE BETTER.

04:47.418 --> 04:49.420
YEAH, THAT'S ACTUALLY
WHY I STOPPED BY.

04:49.420 --> 04:51.762
I WANTED TO BRING YOU
UP TO SPEED.

04:51.762 --> 04:55.696
THERE WAS A 911 CALL
FROM RICKFORD'S HOUSE

04:55.696 --> 04:57.027
RIGHT
BEFORE THE SHOOTING.

04:57.027 --> 04:58.799
WOMAN: 911.
What's your emergency?

04:58.799 --> 05:00.671
BLAKE: There's a crazy woman
stalking me.

05:00.671 --> 05:03.604
She just broke into my house.
Please send help.

05:03.604 --> 05:05.536
I-I think she's got a gun.
She's gonna kill me.

05:05.536 --> 05:08.639
THIS DOESN'T EXACTLY
HELP YOUR EX'S CASE.

05:08.639 --> 05:10.811
RICKFORD KNEW HE WAS ABOUT
TO GET CAUGHT RAPING A WOMAN,

05:10.811 --> 05:13.814
SO HE MADE THAT BOGUS 911 CALL
TO COVER HIS ASS.

05:13.814 --> 05:16.687
YOU FIND THE WOMAN
HE WAS TRYING TO RAPE,

05:16.687 --> 05:18.389
AND SHE'LL TELL YOU THAT CALL
WAS A LOAD OF CRAP.

05:18.389 --> 05:19.950
SHE CAME FORWARD
THIS MORNING.

05:19.950 --> 05:22.553
HER NAME IS WENDY BURRELL.
I'M ABOUT TO GO INTERVIEW HER.

05:22.553 --> 05:24.425
GREAT. I'LL SIT IN.

05:24.425 --> 05:26.797
LOOK, I GET IT.
IF I WERE IN YOUR SHOES,

05:26.797 --> 05:28.629
I'D HAVE WORMED MY WAY
INTO THE CASE ANY WAY I COULD.

05:28.629 --> 05:30.831
SO, AS A PROFESSIONAL COURTESY,
I'M GIVING YOU A HEADS-UP,

05:30.831 --> 05:32.903
BUT YOU KNOW I CAN'T LET YOU
TALK TO THE WITNESS.

05:32.903 --> 05:37.408
BUT AS A PROFESSIONAL COURTESY,
YOU COULD LET ME LISTEN.

05:37.408 --> 05:38.969
[ CHUCKLES ]

05:38.969 --> 05:41.341
I'M DESIGNING A MEDIA ROOM
FOR THIS FINANCE GUY

05:41.341 --> 05:43.974
AND HE WANTS TO SEE
SOME LEATHER SWATCHES
FOR A SECTIONAL.

05:43.974 --> 05:47.648
SO, I WAS WAITING AT THE BAR
WHEN HE TEXTED AND BLEW ME OFF.

05:47.648 --> 05:50.681
THEN THIS CUTE GUY COMES UP
AND OFFERS TO BUY ME A DRINK.

05:50.681 --> 05:52.553
BLAKE RICKFORD?
MM-HMM.

05:52.553 --> 05:55.456
DID YOU FEEL, UM -- I DON'T
KNOW -- UNUSUAL IN ANY WAY?

05:55.456 --> 05:57.458
UM, WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

05:57.458 --> 05:58.759
WELL, THERE WAS A WITNESS
AT THE BAR

05:58.759 --> 06:00.691
THAT SAID THAT
YOU MIGHT HAVE BEEN DRUGGED.

06:00.691 --> 06:02.393
NO WAY.
[ CHUCKLES ]

06:02.393 --> 06:05.936
I SKIPPED LUNCH,
SO I GOT BUZZED PRETTY QUICK,

06:05.936 --> 06:08.098
BUT I WASN'T SO DRUNK
I DIDN'T KNOW WHAT I WAS DOING,

06:08.098 --> 06:10.641
IF THAT'S
WHY YOU'RE ASKING.

06:10.641 --> 06:12.873
WHOSE IDEA WAS IT
TO GO BACK TO HIS PLACE?

06:12.873 --> 06:14.775
MINE.

06:16.547 --> 06:17.948
I WAS GONNA FOLLOW HIM,

06:17.948 --> 06:20.110
BUT HE CONVINCED ME
I WAS IN NO SHAPE TO DRIVE.

06:20.110 --> 06:21.712
HE WAS A GENTLEMAN.

06:21.712 --> 06:23.914
PROMISED TO BRING ME BACK
TO MY CAR IN THE MORNING.

06:23.914 --> 06:26.487
WHAT HAPPENED
AT HIS PLACE?

06:26.487 --> 06:29.820
I DON'T USUALLY DO IT
ON THE FIRST DATE,

06:29.820 --> 06:32.593
BUT I THOUGHT
HE WAS A CATCH.

06:32.593 --> 06:33.764
SO, IT WAS CONSENSUAL?

06:33.764 --> 06:35.065
TOTALLY.

06:35.065 --> 06:36.967
DID HE HURT YOU IN ANY WAY?
NO.

06:36.967 --> 06:39.970
I MEAN, HE THREW ME ON THE BED,
BUT THAT WAS HOT.

06:39.970 --> 06:41.802
DID YOU SCREAM?

06:41.802 --> 06:43.403
[ LAUGHING ]

06:43.403 --> 06:47.407
WELL, MAYBE I SQUEALED.
IT WAS EXCITING.

06:49.139 --> 06:50.811
UNTIL I HEARD SOMEONE
BREAKING IN.

06:50.811 --> 06:52.913
[ GLASS SHATTERS ]

06:52.913 --> 06:54.745
HE TELLS ME
HE'S GOT A STALKER.

06:54.745 --> 06:56.987
COULD HAVE MENTIONED THAT BEFORE
I WENT HOME WITH HIM, RIGHT?

06:56.987 --> 07:01.992
HE GRABS A GUN FROM
THE NIGHTSTAND, AND I FREAK.

07:01.992 --> 07:06.827
I WENT DOWN THE BACK STAIRS,
AND I JUST KEPT RUNNING.

07:06.827 --> 07:09.700
THANK YOU VERY MUCH,
MISS BURRELL.

07:11.632 --> 07:13.103
[ DOOR OPENS ]

07:14.635 --> 07:17.437
I AM REALLY SORRY,
RYAN.

07:17.437 --> 07:18.869
I WAS HOPING
IT WOULDN'T GO THIS WAY,

07:18.869 --> 07:21.572
BUT I'M SWEARING OUT A WARRANT
FOR MORETTI'S ARREST...

07:21.572 --> 07:22.743
FOR MURDER.

07:33.453 --> 07:36.627
Judge Cabrera: THE UNITED STATES
vs. KATHERINE ROSE MORETTI.

07:36.627 --> 07:38.458
COUNSELORS,
YOUR APPEARANCES, PLEASE.

07:39.860 --> 07:42.032
A.U.S.A. TODD ERLICH
FOR THE GOVERNMENT, YOUR HONOR.

07:42.032 --> 07:45.135
DONALD RYAN FOR THE DEFENSE,
YOUR HONOR.

07:45.135 --> 07:47.097
Judge Cabrera:
IF I'M NOT MISTAKEN, MR. RYAN,

07:47.097 --> 07:48.999
YOU'RE AN ASSISTANT
UNITED STATES ATTORNEY.

07:48.999 --> 07:50.671
I WAS.
I JUST RESIGNED.

07:52.172 --> 07:53.804
DONNIE, WHAT THE HELL
ARE YOU DOING?
COME ON, KATE.

07:53.804 --> 07:55.606
WHO COULD DEFEND YOU
BETTER THAN ME?

07:56.947 --> 07:58.809
THANKS. DON'T WORRY.
YOU'LL STILL GET YOUR CHECK.

07:58.809 --> 08:01.481
LET'S PROCEED.

08:01.481 --> 08:03.814
THE DEFENDANT IS CHARGED WITH
MURDER IN THE SECOND DEGREE.

08:03.814 --> 08:06.657
HOW DO YOU PLEAD?
NOT GUILTY, YOUR HONOR.

08:06.657 --> 08:08.488
I'LL HEAR THE GOVERNMENT
ON BAIL.

08:08.488 --> 08:09.660
WE ASK FOR REMAND.

08:09.660 --> 08:11.522
MY CLIENT'S
NOT A FLIGHT RISK.

08:11.522 --> 08:13.524
SHE'S A DECORATED
LAW-ENFORCEMENT OFFICER

08:13.524 --> 08:15.696
WHO WELCOMES THE CHANCE
TO CLEAR HER GOOD NAME.

08:15.696 --> 08:18.529
WE ASK YOU TO RELEASE
AGENT MORETTI ON HER
OWN RECOGNIZANCE.

08:18.529 --> 08:20.531
MS. MORETTI WAS SUSPENDED
FROM THE FBI

08:20.531 --> 08:22.032
FOR HARASSING THE DECEASED.

08:22.032 --> 08:23.904
SHE FORFEITED HER GOOD NAME

08:23.904 --> 08:26.236
WHEN SHE WENT ROGUE
AND KILLED A MAN.

08:26.236 --> 08:28.078
Judge Cabrera: WHAT DO YOU SAY
I SPLIT THE BABY

08:28.078 --> 08:30.581
AND ORDER THE DEFENDANT
RELEASED ON HOUSE ARREST?

08:30.581 --> 08:33.714
YOU WILL WEAR
AN ELECTRONIC MONITORING DEVICE,

08:33.714 --> 08:36.046
AND YOU CAN ONLY LEAVE HOME
TO GO TO THERAPY

08:36.046 --> 08:37.247
OR TO YOUR ATTORNEY'S OFFICE.

08:44.995 --> 08:48.158
YOUR CRAZY EX-WIFE
IS GOING DOWN.

08:48.158 --> 08:51.101
YOU BE CAREFUL.
SHE'LL BRING YOU DOWN WITH HER.

08:55.736 --> 08:57.267
WELL, THE GOOD NEWS IS

08:57.267 --> 08:59.139
IF I CAN'T HIT THE BILLY GOAT
FOR BURGERS AND FRIES,

08:59.139 --> 09:00.841
I'LL PROBABLY
LOSE 10 POUNDS.

09:00.841 --> 09:02.713
NOT TO MENTION
YOUR HIGH CHOLESTEROL.

09:02.713 --> 09:04.575
SHOULD HAVE SLAPPED ONE OF THOSE
ON YOU YEARS AGO.

09:04.575 --> 09:06.246
RYAN.

09:06.246 --> 09:08.979
I GOT TO ADMIT,
IT'S A PRETTY BALLSY MOVE.

09:08.979 --> 09:12.052
WHAT DO YOU WANT, ERLICH?
PLEAD GUILTY
TO INVOLUNTARY MANSLAUGHTER.

09:12.052 --> 09:14.054
YOU'LL SERVE 3 TO 5.
OTHERWISE, WE GO TO TRIAL.

09:14.054 --> 09:15.826
YOU HAVE TILL FRIDAY
TO DECIDE.

09:15.826 --> 09:18.629
I DON'T NEED TILL FRIDAY.
NO DEAL.

09:18.629 --> 09:19.630
[ ELEVATOR BELL DINGS ]

09:24.294 --> 09:26.166
SO, THIS IS
THE MAN CAVE?

09:26.166 --> 09:28.869
UH, NOT ANYMORE.

09:28.869 --> 09:33.043
WELCOME TO THE LAW OFFICES
OF DONALD RYAN, ESQUIRE.

09:33.043 --> 09:35.305
PLEASE, SIT DOWN.

09:35.305 --> 09:39.179
[ SIGHS ]

09:39.179 --> 09:42.853
ALL RIGHT.
LET'S TALK STRATEGY.

09:42.853 --> 09:44.855
I GOT A STRATEGY.

09:44.855 --> 09:47.017
I TELL THE TRUTH.
THE MURDER CHARGE IS BULLSHIT.

09:47.017 --> 09:49.359
IT'S TRUMPED UP UNDER PRESSURE
FROM CONGRESSMAN RICKFORD.

09:49.359 --> 09:52.092
I SAVED THAT WOMAN
FROM BEING RAPED.

09:52.092 --> 09:54.064
THAT'S NOT
WHAT WENDY BURRELL SAYS.

09:54.064 --> 09:55.265
YEAH, WELL, SHE'S LYING.

09:55.265 --> 09:56.797
INTERIOR DECORATOR,
NO RECORD,

09:56.797 --> 09:58.669
A NICE GIRL
WITH NO CONNECTION

09:58.669 --> 10:00.170
TO BLAKE RICKFORD
BEFORE THAT NIGHT.

10:00.170 --> 10:01.371
WHY WOULD SHE LIE?

10:01.371 --> 10:02.903
RAPE
IS A TRAUMATIC EVENT.

10:02.903 --> 10:04.705
PEOPLE REACT TO IT
IN DIFFERENT WAYS.

10:04.705 --> 10:06.707
SHE'S A STRONG,
INDEPENDENT WOMAN.

10:06.707 --> 10:08.709
MAYBE SHE DIDN'T
WANT TO BE SEEN AS A VICTIM.

10:09.940 --> 10:11.882
LOOK,
I KNOW WHAT I SAW.

10:11.882 --> 10:13.283
ACTUALLY,
MAYBE YOU DON'T.

10:14.344 --> 10:18.118
YOUR PERCEPTION OF WHAT HAPPENED
MAY HAVE BEEN DISTORTED.

10:18.118 --> 10:19.820
UH, S-SPACIAL
AND TEMPORAL CONFUSION

10:19.820 --> 10:21.992
IS -- IS COMMON
IN OFFICER-INVOLVED SHOOTINGS.

10:21.992 --> 10:23.323
OKAY, HEY.
BREAK IT DOWN FOR US.

10:23.323 --> 10:24.955
AFTER KILLING A SUSPECT,

10:24.955 --> 10:27.027
COPS O-O-OFTEN REPORT
TIMELINES AND GEOGRAPHY

10:27.027 --> 10:28.959
THAT -- THAT PROVES
TOTALLY WRONG.

10:28.959 --> 10:32.032
A-A DISTANCE OF 5 FEET
IS DESCRIBED AS 50.

10:32.032 --> 10:34.735
I DON'T NEED A NEUROSCIENTIST
TO PROVE THAT COPS LIE.

10:34.735 --> 10:36.206
IT'S NOT ABOUT LYING.

10:36.206 --> 10:37.738
THE STRESS OF THE SITUATION
MAY HAVE CAUSED KATE

10:37.738 --> 10:39.740
TO REMEMBER EVENTS
NOT AS THEY HAPPENED,

10:39.740 --> 10:41.872
BUT IN A WAY THAT FITS
WITH HER PRECONCEIVED NOTION

10:41.872 --> 10:44.214
THAT RICKFORD IS A RAPIST.
GREAT. THAT I CAN USE.

10:44.214 --> 10:47.778
HOW? HE'S BASICALLY SAYING
THAT I'M GUILTY AND CRAZY.

10:47.778 --> 10:51.121
NO, HE'S SAYING WENDY'S
TESTIMONY DOESN'T EVEN MATTER.

10:51.121 --> 10:54.654
IF YOU HAD A REASONABLE BELIEF
THAT RICKFORD

10:54.654 --> 10:56.326
WAS RAPING A WOMAN,
YOU MAY HAVE BEEN WRONG,

10:56.326 --> 10:57.958
BUT YOU WOULDN'T
BE CRIMINALLY LIABLE.

10:59.659 --> 11:01.361
THAT'S GOOD.
IT'S VERY GOOD.

11:01.361 --> 11:05.135
BUT FIRST WE'D HAVE TO PROVE
THAT RICKFORD WAS A RAPIST.

11:05.135 --> 11:07.698
WE HAVE KENDRA MURPHY.
MAYBE HE RAPED OTHER SOLDIERS.

11:07.698 --> 11:10.170
I MEAN, A-A GUY LIKE THAT
DOESN'T HAVE JUST ONE VICTIM.

11:10.170 --> 11:12.002
ANYTHING THAT HAPPENED
IN AFGHANISTAN

11:12.002 --> 11:13.373
IS OUTSIDE
OUR JURISDICTION.

11:13.373 --> 11:14.975
THAT'S A PROSECUTOR'S
PROBLEM.

11:14.975 --> 11:17.147
I'M A FULLY FLEDGED MEMBER
OF THE DEFENSE BAR

11:17.147 --> 11:19.349
TRYING TO DIRTY UP
A HOMICIDE VICTIM ANY WAY I CAN.

11:19.349 --> 11:20.450
THAT'S KIND OF SICK.

11:21.852 --> 11:23.683
I LIKE IT.

11:24.785 --> 11:27.287
I WILL TALK TO EVERY SOLDIER

11:27.287 --> 11:30.060
WHO SERVED ALONGSIDE RICKFORD
IN THE GUARD.

11:30.060 --> 11:31.762
DANIEL, GET ME
ALL THE RESEARCH YOU CAN

11:31.762 --> 11:33.263
ON THIS
"PERCEPTION DISTORTION" THING.

11:33.263 --> 11:34.825
WHAT DO I DO?

11:34.825 --> 11:37.297
UM...MAKE A FILE OF EVERYTHING
YOU CAN REMEMBER

11:37.297 --> 11:39.199
ABOUT THE NIGHT
OF THE SHOOTING.

11:39.199 --> 11:42.032
SO, BASICALLY SIT AROUND
AND DO NOTHING.

11:42.032 --> 11:44.704
WELL, THANKS TO
THE FASHION ACCESSORY THERE,

11:44.704 --> 11:47.077
YOU DON'T HAVE
MUCH OF A CHOICE.

11:49.009 --> 11:52.783
HEY. THERE'S MY GIRL.
[ CHUCKLES ]

11:52.783 --> 11:54.284
DAD,
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

11:54.284 --> 11:55.415
OH, YOU CAN'T GO OUT,

11:55.415 --> 11:57.017
SO I THOUGHT
WE'D HAVE A MOVIE NIGHT.

11:57.017 --> 11:59.289
I GOT YOUR FAVORITES --
"FRENCH CONNECTION,"

11:59.289 --> 12:02.492
UH, "TAKING OF PELHAM
ONE TWO THREE."
OKAY, THOSE ARE YOUR FAVORITES.

12:02.492 --> 12:05.255
THE ORIGINAL --
NOT THAT GOD-AWFUL REMAKE.

12:05.255 --> 12:08.058
MOVIE NIGHT IS A GREAT IDEA.
I JUST CAN'T RIGHT NOW.

12:08.058 --> 12:09.399
I HAVE SO MUCH WORK TO DO,

12:09.399 --> 12:11.932
AND DONNIE NEEDS ME
TO WRITE UP THIS REPORT.

12:11.932 --> 12:13.503
UM, HOW ABOUT
TOMORROW NIGHT?

12:15.035 --> 12:16.366
SURE.

12:18.338 --> 12:21.872
I, UH, WISH THERE WAS
SOMETHING I COULD DO

12:21.872 --> 12:23.473
BESIDES BRING YOU
DUMB MOVIES.

12:23.473 --> 12:25.075
[ CHUCKLES ]

12:25.075 --> 12:28.048
YOU ARE MY LITTLE GIRL.
IT'S MY JOB TO PROTECT YOU.

12:28.048 --> 12:30.050
YOU'RE DOING JUST FINE.

12:30.050 --> 12:33.483
YEAH. WELL, YOU CALL ME
IF YOU NEED ANYTHING.

12:33.483 --> 12:34.885
LOVE YOU, KIDDO.

12:34.885 --> 12:36.026
LOVE YOU, DAD.

12:58.208 --> 12:59.549
[ DOG BARKING IN DISTANCE ]

13:10.020 --> 13:11.892
HEY, RICKFORD.

13:16.166 --> 13:17.868
Blake:
WHOA, WHOA, PLEASE.

13:17.868 --> 13:20.100
PLEASE, DON'T --
DON'T KILL ME.

13:20.800 --> 13:23.073
[ GASPS ]

13:23.073 --> 13:25.575
[ PANTING ]

13:25.575 --> 13:27.577
I KNOW WHAT I SAW THAT NIGHT.

13:27.577 --> 13:29.309
THIS WHOLE THING
IS BULLSHIT.

13:29.309 --> 13:31.011
YOU SOUND ANGRY.
YOU THINK?

13:31.011 --> 13:33.343
I STOPPED A SCUMBAG
FROM RAPING A WOMAN.

13:33.343 --> 13:35.886
AND WHAT DO I GET?
ARRESTED.

13:35.886 --> 13:38.949
DRAGGED INTO COURT,
AND LOCKED UP IN MY APARTMENT.

13:40.390 --> 13:43.423
THE ICING ON THE FREAKING CAKE
IS THAT DANIEL PIERCE,

13:43.423 --> 13:46.596
WHO I HAVE BELIEVED EVERY TIME
HE HAD SOME CRAZY THEORY,

13:46.596 --> 13:49.099
WHO I HAVE FOLLOWED OUT
ONTO MORE LIMBS

13:49.099 --> 13:50.530
THAN I CAN EVEN COUNT,

13:50.530 --> 13:52.863
THINKS THAT I IMAGINED
THE WHOLE THING.

13:52.863 --> 13:55.035
SO, YEAH,
I'M A LITTLE BIT PISSED.

13:55.035 --> 13:58.038
YOU'VE BEEN DREAMING
ABOUT THE SHOOTING.

14:00.010 --> 14:01.872
HOW DID YOU KNOW?

14:01.872 --> 14:04.044
WELL, YOU'RE NOT THE FIRST COP
I'VE EVER TREATED.

14:04.044 --> 14:05.275
TELL ME ABOUT IT.

14:10.450 --> 14:13.323
I DREAMT THAT I KILLED HIM
IN COLD BLOOD

14:13.323 --> 14:17.988
AND THAT HE...
HE BEGGED FOR HIS LIFE.

14:17.988 --> 14:22.332
YOUR FILE SAYS YOU RETURNED FIRE
AFTER HE SHOT AT YOU.

14:22.332 --> 14:26.866
I'VE BEEN GOING OVER IT
AND OVER IT IN MY MIND,

14:26.866 --> 14:32.542
AND, UH...
AND NOW I'M JUST...

14:32.542 --> 14:34.905
I'M QUESTIONING
EVERYTHING I SAW.

14:34.905 --> 14:37.347
I MEAN, I SAW HIM
STIRRING HER DRINK,

14:37.347 --> 14:41.151
BUT THIS GUY
WAS HITTING ON ME,

14:41.151 --> 14:44.314
SO I GUESS I NEVER ACTUALLY
SAW HIM PUT ANYTHING IN IT.

14:44.314 --> 14:46.216
MAYBE HE DIDN'T DRUG HER.

14:46.216 --> 14:48.989
MAYBE SHE DID
WANT TO GO WITH HIM.

14:48.989 --> 14:50.660
[ CELLPHONE VIBRATES ]

14:50.660 --> 14:55.125
I FORGOT THAT I WAS DISTRACTED
FOR A SECOND BY A PHONE CALL.

14:57.527 --> 15:01.471
MAYBE SHE WAS INTO HIM.

15:03.974 --> 15:06.576
MAYBE HE WAS AFRAID OF ME
WHEN I BURST INTO THAT ROOM.

15:11.011 --> 15:14.684
I WAS JUST SO SURE
THAT HE WAS ATTACKING WENDY.

15:14.684 --> 15:17.287
WHY?
BECAUSE I KNOW
THAT HE RAPED KENDRA.

15:17.287 --> 15:21.151
KENDRA IS A SICK WOMAN WITH
A SEVERE NEUROLOGICAL ILLNESS.

15:21.151 --> 15:23.453
CAN YOU REALLY TRUST
HER STORY?

15:30.961 --> 15:34.464
SO, I WAS WRONG...

15:34.464 --> 15:37.207
ABOUT EVERYTHING?

15:37.207 --> 15:40.610
WHAT IF YOU WERE?

15:42.642 --> 15:45.515
THEN I KILLED A MAN
FOR NO REASON.

16:00.730 --> 16:03.033
[ SIGHS ]
WHAT DO YOU WANT, DANIEL?

16:03.033 --> 16:05.535
TO TELL YOU
THE TRUTH.

16:05.535 --> 16:07.137
ABOUT WHAT?

16:07.137 --> 16:09.339
WHY I BROKE UP WITH YOU
ALL THOSE YEARS AGO.

16:09.339 --> 16:11.201
I'M LISTENING.

16:13.573 --> 16:16.546
WHEN YOU WENT
BACK TO YOUR FOLKS' PLACE

16:16.546 --> 16:19.449
TO TALK ABOUT VIENNA,
I WAS MISERABLE.

16:19.449 --> 16:21.711
COULDN'T EAT,
COULDN'T SLEEP.

16:21.711 --> 16:25.055
PAUL CONVINCED ME
TO GO ON A ROAD TRIP.

16:27.687 --> 16:31.561
AND WE WENT TO SPRING FLING
AT MICHIGAN,

16:31.561 --> 16:36.666
ENDED UP AT A PARTY...
AND I MET THIS GIRL.

16:38.398 --> 16:41.731
WE LIKED THE SAME BOOKS,
SAME BANDS.

16:41.731 --> 16:43.433
AND IN 20 MINUTES,

16:43.433 --> 16:46.076
WE WERE FINISHING
EACH OTHER'S SENTENCES.

16:46.076 --> 16:49.239
AND I THOUGHT YOU WERE SO NOBLE
BREAKING UP WITH ME

16:49.239 --> 16:50.710
SO I'D GO TO VIENNA.

16:50.710 --> 16:54.144
I SHOULD HAVE KNOWN
YOU'D DUMP ME FOR ANOTHER GIRL.

16:59.419 --> 17:00.750
IT'S NOT THAT SIMPLE.

17:00.750 --> 17:02.122
REALLY,
I DON'T NEED TO KNOW.

17:02.122 --> 17:03.653
YES, YOU DO.

17:03.653 --> 17:06.356
HER NAME IS NATALIE.

17:08.328 --> 17:10.330
WE'RE STILL TOGETHER.

17:10.330 --> 17:13.032
YOU'RE MARRIED?

17:13.032 --> 17:15.465
NO.
I'M SCHIZOPHRENIC.

17:15.465 --> 17:17.767
I KNOW, DANIEL.
AND I UNDERSTAND.

17:17.767 --> 17:20.240
NO, YOU DON'T.
NOT EVERYTHING.

17:21.571 --> 17:26.116
NATALIE AND I, WE'RE --
S-SHE -- SHE'S NOT...

17:26.116 --> 17:30.780
[ CHUCKLES ]
SHE'S NOT REAL.

17:33.123 --> 17:36.726
NATALIE'S
A HALLUCINATION.

17:36.726 --> 17:40.190
I LEFT YOU FOR A WOMAN
THAT DOESN'T EXIST.

17:43.433 --> 17:48.138
I WAS CRAZY THEN,
AND I'M CRAZY NOW.

17:48.138 --> 17:51.471
AND THAT'S WHY
WE CAN'T BE TOGETHER.

17:57.277 --> 18:00.280
SO, WHAT WILL YOU DO
IF YOU DON'T GET YOUR JOB BACK?

18:00.280 --> 18:02.512
OH, YOU MEAN
IF I DON'T GO TO PRISON?

18:02.512 --> 18:06.156
TRY ANSWERING
WITHOUT A SNAPPY COMEBACK.

18:08.758 --> 18:11.291
WHEN I WAS 7,
MY MOM DIED.

18:11.291 --> 18:13.293
MY DAD
WAS WORKING HOMICIDE.

18:13.293 --> 18:16.196
CRAZY, CRAZY HOURS.
HE WAS NEVER, EVER HOME.

18:16.196 --> 18:19.399
SO, MY AUNT CLAIRE
ACTUALLY OFFERED TO TAKE ME IN,

18:19.399 --> 18:20.700
BUT MY DAD SAID NO,

18:20.700 --> 18:23.333
THAT IT WOULD KILL HIM
TO LOSE ME, TOO.

18:23.333 --> 18:24.874
SO,
HOW DID HE MANAGE IT?

18:24.874 --> 18:28.408
THE SCHOOL BUS WOULD DROP ME OFF
AT THE PRECINCT.

18:28.408 --> 18:30.810
I'D DO MY HOMEWORK
IN THE BULLPEN.

18:30.810 --> 18:32.342
AND THAT WAS OKAY
WITH YOU?

18:32.342 --> 18:33.613
IT WAS BETTER THAN OKAY.

18:33.613 --> 18:35.385
I MEAN,
ALL THE OTHER GIRLS,

18:35.385 --> 18:37.547
THEY HAD TO GO TO BALLET
OR GYMNASTICS.

18:37.547 --> 18:39.819
I GOT TO WATCH
REAL LIVE INTERROGATIONS --

18:39.819 --> 18:42.252
BETTER THAN ANYTHING
YOU COULD SEE ON TV.

18:44.494 --> 18:50.830
I'VE WORKED MY ENTIRE LIFE
TO GET WHERE I'VE GOTTEN.

18:52.632 --> 18:54.634
SO...

18:54.634 --> 18:58.638
IF I CAN'T BE
A COP ANYMORE, UM...

19:00.810 --> 19:03.513
...I DON'T KNOW WHO I AM.

19:05.545 --> 19:07.547
Carlos:
I'M SORRY RICKFORD'S DEAD.

19:07.547 --> 19:09.279
BUT HE WAS
THE KIND OF DIRTBAG

19:09.279 --> 19:11.721
THAT GIVES THE MILITARY
A BAD NAME.
HOW SO?

19:11.721 --> 19:14.784
HE BLEW OFF WEEKEND TRAINING,
SHIRKED DUTY ON BASE.

19:14.784 --> 19:16.686
HE WAS ALWAYS
MAKING CRUDE JOKES,

19:16.686 --> 19:18.828
COULDN'T LOOK AT ME
ABOVE THE NECK.

19:18.828 --> 19:21.861
HE DO MORE THAN LOOK?
IF YOU'RE ASKING IF HE RAPED ME,
THE ANSWER IS NO, SIR.

19:21.861 --> 19:23.863
BUT ONCE HE GRABBED MY ASS
IN THE CHOW LINE,

19:23.863 --> 19:25.395
AND THE LOOK ON HIS FACE

19:25.395 --> 19:27.937
MADE ME WANT TO SLEEP
WITH MY WEAPON FOR A WEEK.

19:27.937 --> 19:30.700
HE GIVE ANYONE ELSE
A HARD TIME?
JUST ABOUT EVERY WOMAN
ON THE BASE.

19:30.700 --> 19:34.844
WE LEAVE OUR FAMILIES, OUR JOBS,
OUR LIVES TO SERVE.

19:34.844 --> 19:36.846
Carlos: WE HAD ENOUGH TROUBLE
WITH THE TALIBAN.

19:36.846 --> 19:38.808
WE DIDN'T NEED JERKS LIKE HIM
HASSLING WOMEN.

19:38.808 --> 19:40.710
DID HE HASSLE
ANYONE SPECIFIC?

19:40.710 --> 19:42.482
GABRIELLE BLAIR
HATED HIS GUTS.

19:42.482 --> 19:44.654
MAYBE HE TRIED
SOMETHING ON HER,

19:44.654 --> 19:47.287
BUT SHE'S NOT
GONNA TALK TO YOU.

19:49.289 --> 19:52.462
GABRIELLE WAS TWO WEEKS
FROM COMING HOME

19:52.462 --> 19:55.625
WHEN HER CONVOY WAS ATTACKED
IN THE QALAT VALLEY.

19:55.625 --> 19:58.868
THE SPINAL-CORD INJURY
LEFT HER QUADRIPLEGIC.

19:58.868 --> 20:00.630
THAT SHOULDN'T AFFECT
HER SPEECH.

20:00.630 --> 20:02.572
THE V.A. DOC SAYS
IT'S PSYCHOLOGICAL --

20:02.572 --> 20:05.535
THAT SHE'S BEEN TRAUMATIZED
BY WHAT'S HAPPENED TO HER,

20:05.535 --> 20:07.307
LIKE SHELL SHOCK.

20:07.307 --> 20:10.840
SHE JUST SITS ALL DAY LONG,
STARING AT THE GARDEN.

20:10.840 --> 20:13.843
PTSD AND DEPRESSION.

20:13.843 --> 20:18.448
IT'S POSSIBLE THAT'S
CAUSING HER SILENCE.

20:21.691 --> 20:23.323
BUT I DON'T THINK SO.

20:24.624 --> 20:26.326
GABRIELLE?

20:26.326 --> 20:28.998
MY NAME'S
DR. DANIEL PIERCE.

20:28.998 --> 20:30.800
CAN YOU UNDERSTAND ME?

20:30.800 --> 20:33.232
I TOLD YOU.

20:33.232 --> 20:34.904
IS YOUR SISTER
RIGHT-HANDED?

20:34.904 --> 20:36.736
YES, BUT WHAT DOES THAT
HAVE TO DO WITH ANYTHING?

20:36.736 --> 20:40.610
I WANT TO TALK
ABOUT BLAKE RICKFORD.

20:40.610 --> 20:42.312
I THINK HE WAS A BAD GUY.

20:42.312 --> 20:43.643
I HAVE A LOT OF QUESTIONS
ABOUT HIM,

20:43.643 --> 20:45.845
MAYBE YOU
HAVE THE ANSWERS.

20:45.845 --> 20:49.018
I KNOW YOU CAN'T TALK.

20:49.018 --> 20:51.351
BUT MAYBE YOU CAN SING.

20:51.351 --> 20:53.683
SING?
WHAT IS HE TALKING ABOUT?

20:53.683 --> 20:55.955
I THINK
YOU WERE MISDIAGNOSED.

20:55.955 --> 20:58.688
YOU MAY HAVE SOMETHING
CALLED BROCA'S APHASIA.

20:58.688 --> 21:00.860
THE DROOP ON THE LEFT SIDE
OF YOUR FACE TELLS ME

21:00.860 --> 21:02.662
THAT THE LEFT HEMISPHERE
OF YOUR BRAIN

21:02.662 --> 21:04.364
HAS BEEN INJURED.

21:04.364 --> 21:07.266
THAT'S THE SIDE THAT WE --
WE USE TO SPEAK OR TO WRITE.

21:07.266 --> 21:08.468
BUT SINGING,

21:08.468 --> 21:10.400
THAT'S THE RIGHT SIDE
OF OUR BRAIN.

21:12.642 --> 21:14.344
YOU KNOW THE SONG
"CLEMENTINE"?

21:16.346 --> 21:18.348
♪ OH, MY DARLING,
OH, MY DARLING ♪

21:18.348 --> 21:20.810
♪ OH,
MY DARLING, CLEMENTINE ♪

21:20.810 --> 21:23.913
USE THAT MELODY
AND SING TO ME.

21:26.586 --> 21:28.618
♪ OH, MY DARLING ♪

21:30.860 --> 21:33.423
♪ COME ON, DARLING ♪

21:35.865 --> 21:37.767
♪ WHAT'S YOUR NAME,
DEAR? ♪

21:40.530 --> 21:42.702
♪ GABRIELLE ♪

21:42.702 --> 21:45.405
[ GASPS ]

21:55.084 --> 21:59.018
YOU'RE DOING GREAT, GABRIELLE.
HERE'S WHERE I NEED HELP.

21:59.018 --> 22:00.890
[ To the tune of "Clementine" ]
♪ YOU HAD A PROBLEM ♪

22:00.890 --> 22:03.052
♪ WITH BLAKE RICKFORD ♪

22:03.052 --> 22:04.924
♪ WHAT WAS IT? ♪

22:08.798 --> 22:11.561
DID HE RAPE YOU?

22:11.561 --> 22:14.534
[ To the tune of "Clementine" ]
♪ NO, HE DIDN'T ♪

22:17.066 --> 22:19.068
♪ WAIT, THERE'S MORE ♪

22:20.410 --> 22:22.542
♪ IT WAS A CONVOY ♪

22:22.542 --> 22:24.914
♪ ON A MISSION ♪

22:24.914 --> 22:29.619
♪ I WAS DRIVING
THE HUMVEE ♪

22:29.619 --> 22:34.123
♪ KENDRA WAS THERE
AND THE C.O. ♪

22:34.123 --> 22:36.826
♪ AND BLAKE RICKFORD
WAS THERE, TOO ♪

22:38.528 --> 22:40.089
[ EXPLOSION ]

22:43.663 --> 22:47.637
♪ TALIBAN
SHOT OUR GUNNER ♪

22:54.373 --> 22:55.645
I THINK HE'S DEAD, SIR!

22:55.645 --> 22:57.547
RICKFORD,
TAKE OVER THE 240.

22:57.547 --> 22:58.908
[ GUNFIRE ]

22:58.908 --> 23:00.880
SERGEANT,
GET UP THERE!

23:00.880 --> 23:02.812
I GOT IT, SIR.

23:02.812 --> 23:05.815
♪ AND KENDRA,
SHE WENT UP ♪

23:07.557 --> 23:10.119
RICKFORD, GET YOUR ASS OUT
OF THIS VEHICLE AND RETURN FIRE,

23:10.119 --> 23:11.721
NOW!

23:16.826 --> 23:18.728
TROOPS IN CONTACT!
TROOPS IN CONTACT!

23:18.728 --> 23:20.470
REQUEST IMMEDIATE
FIRE MISSION.

23:22.732 --> 23:27.837
FIRE ONE H.E. ROUND
AT GRID ECHO GULF 30262640.

23:27.837 --> 23:29.779
I'LL ADJUST, OVER.

23:29.779 --> 23:32.111
WAIT. NO!

23:32.111 --> 23:35.815
♪ THE C.O.
MADE AN ERROR ♪

23:35.815 --> 23:39.148
♪ CALLED IN
WRONG COORDINATES ♪

23:46.726 --> 23:49.859
IT WAS FRIENDLY FIRE.

23:51.631 --> 23:54.964
SO, THE C.O. AND YOU, YOU WERE
THE ONLY ONES IN THE HUMVEE?

23:54.964 --> 23:56.205
DID ANYONE ELSE KNOW?

23:57.537 --> 23:59.539
♪ I GOT OUT
TO CALL FOR HELP ♪

23:59.539 --> 24:00.540
COVER ME.

24:00.540 --> 24:01.771
THE C.O. SCREWED UP.

24:01.771 --> 24:03.473
CALLED IN A STRIKE
ON OUR POSITION.

24:03.473 --> 24:04.714
HE DID WHAT?

24:04.714 --> 24:08.548
♪ I GOT MAD
AND YELLED AT BLAKE ♪

24:08.548 --> 24:10.750
YOU HEARD ME!
STAND UP, RICKFORD!

24:10.750 --> 24:13.052
GET OFF YOUR ASS
AND RETURN FIRE!

24:13.052 --> 24:14.784
[ EXPLOSION ]

24:20.530 --> 24:24.534
THANK YOU, GABRIELLE.
YOU DID A GREAT JOB.

24:27.036 --> 24:29.038
SO, SHE TELLS RICKFORD
ABOUT THE FRIENDLY FIRE

24:29.038 --> 24:31.200
AND HIS COWARDICE
NEARLY GETS HER KILLED.

24:31.200 --> 24:32.842
GREAT.

24:32.842 --> 24:35.044
SO, WE'VE GOT MORE PROOF
RICKFORD WAS A USELESS WASTE,

24:35.044 --> 24:37.747
BUT WE'RE STILL NO CLOSER
TO SAVING KATE.

24:37.747 --> 24:40.610
FORGET THAT
LILY-LIVERED COWARD.

24:40.610 --> 24:43.953
THE REAL VILLAIN HERE
IS THAT DAMN INCOMPETENT C.O.

24:43.953 --> 24:47.086
THAT BASTARD
KILLED HIS OWN MEN.

24:47.086 --> 24:49.959
WHAT?

24:49.959 --> 24:51.991
WHAT CAN I DO
FOR YOU GENTLEMEN?

24:51.991 --> 24:54.794
WHEN I WAS HERE A FEW DAYS AGO
WITH AGENT MORETTI,

24:54.794 --> 24:56.095
YOU TOLD US
YOU HAD INVESTIGATED

24:56.095 --> 24:57.967
THE RAPE OF A SOLDIER
IN YOUR UNIT --

24:57.967 --> 24:59.498
KENDRA MURPHY.

24:59.498 --> 25:01.500
AS I SAID,
IT WAS UNSUBSTANTIATED.

25:01.500 --> 25:03.232
WE KNOW
BLAKE RICKFORD RAPED HER,

25:03.232 --> 25:04.704
AND WE KNOW
YOU COVERED IT UP.

25:04.704 --> 25:06.776
WHAT?
THAT'S AN OUTRAGEOUS LIE.

25:06.776 --> 25:08.277
GABRIELLE BLAIR
WAS MISDIAGNOSED.

25:08.277 --> 25:10.610
TURNS OUT SHE CAN TALK
AFTER ALL.

25:10.610 --> 25:12.712
YOU'RE GOING DOWN.

25:12.712 --> 25:14.584
TELL US THE TRUTH
AND WE MIGHT BE ABLE TO

25:14.584 --> 25:16.285
MAKE THINGS
A LITTLE EASIER ON YOU.

25:17.887 --> 25:19.589
THE WHOLE STORY
THIS TIME.

25:21.751 --> 25:23.923
A FEW DAYS
AFTER QALAT VALLEY,

25:23.923 --> 25:26.556
KENDRA REPORTED
SHE'D BEEN RAPED BY RICKFORD.

25:26.556 --> 25:28.958
I HAVE TO ASK.
ARE YOU SURE?

25:28.958 --> 25:31.160
WHEN SOMEONE SLAPS ME
ACROSS THE FACE

25:31.160 --> 25:33.162
AND FORCES MY KNEES APART,

25:33.162 --> 25:35.765
I'M PRETTY SURE
THAT'S RAPE...

25:35.765 --> 25:37.266
SIR.

25:37.266 --> 25:40.670
I OPENED AN INVESTIGATION,
STARTING WITH McPHEE AND HICKS,

25:40.670 --> 25:43.613
THE SOLDIERS WHO KENDRA CLAIMED
KNEW ABOUT THE ASSAULT.

25:43.613 --> 25:45.044
BOTH SAID IT NEVER HAPPENED.

25:45.044 --> 25:46.946
AND YOU BELIEVE THEM?
HELL NO.

25:46.946 --> 25:49.619
McPHEE, HICKS, AND RICKFORD
WERE THE THREE AMIGOS.

25:49.619 --> 25:52.281
I KNEW THEY'D LIE FOR HIM.
I HAULED RICKFORD IN.

25:52.281 --> 25:53.923
I'M GONNA COURT-MARTIAL
THE THREE OF YOU --

25:53.923 --> 25:56.125
SEE YOU GET SENT TO LEAVENWORTH.
I DON'T THINK SO.

25:56.125 --> 25:57.887
[ CHUCKLES ]

25:57.887 --> 26:00.229
I DON'T CARE THAT YOUR DADDY'S
ON THE ARMED SERVICES COMMITTEE.

26:00.229 --> 26:02.762
YOU'RE STILL A COWARD
AND A RAPIST.

26:02.762 --> 26:05.164
AND YOU'RE A MURDERER.

26:05.164 --> 26:06.896
YOU GO AFTER ME,

26:06.896 --> 26:09.769
AND I'LL TELL EVERYONE WHAT
REALLY HAPPENED AT QALAT VALLEY.

26:09.769 --> 26:11.901
HOW YOU SHELLED
YOUR OWN POSITION,

26:11.901 --> 26:15.945
KILLED THREE MEN,
AND THEN LIED ABOUT IT.

26:19.178 --> 26:22.251
SO YOU SOLD KENDRA OUT
TO SAVE YOUR OWN ASS.

26:23.212 --> 26:25.755
YOU'LL TESTIFY
AT AGENT MORETTI'S TRIAL,

26:25.755 --> 26:27.717
TELL THE JURY
SHE WAS RIGHT --

26:27.717 --> 26:30.019
BLAKE RICKFORD WAS A RAPIST
AND YOU COVERED IT UP.

26:30.019 --> 26:36.796
WHAT I DID WAS INEXCUSABLE.
WAR POISONS MEN'S SOULS.

26:36.796 --> 26:39.669
GREATEST WAR MOVIE
EVER MADE.

26:39.669 --> 26:42.001
YES, YES. IT'S A QUOTE.

26:42.001 --> 26:44.333
FROM "THE THIN RED LINE."

26:44.333 --> 26:47.206
"WAR POISONS MEN'S SOULS
AND TURNS THEM INTO DOGS."

26:47.206 --> 26:50.379
I TOLD YOU HE KILLED
HIS OWN MEN.

26:50.379 --> 26:53.382
[ SCOFFS ]
I SHOULD HAVE SEEN IT SOONER.

26:53.382 --> 26:54.984
SEEN WHAT?

26:54.984 --> 26:56.916
TWO WITNESSES TO --
TO THE RAPE --

26:56.916 --> 26:58.317
ONE GETS MURDERED,

26:58.317 --> 27:00.619
THE OTHER COMMITS SUICIDE
THEN LEAVES A NOTE

27:00.619 --> 27:02.251
ADMITTING TO KILLING
THE FIRST ONE,

27:02.251 --> 27:05.124
B-B-BUT HICKS DIDN'T LEAVE
THAT INTERNET POST.

27:05.124 --> 27:06.125
YOU DID.

27:06.125 --> 27:07.256
W-WHAT? NO.

27:07.256 --> 27:09.128
YOU USED THE SAME QUOTE,
CAPTAIN.

27:09.128 --> 27:11.160
"WAR POISONS MEN'S SOULS."

27:11.160 --> 27:14.203
WHAT DID YOU TELL YOURSELF?
"HICKS IS A JUNKIE.

27:14.203 --> 27:16.235
"IT'S ONLY A MATTER OF TIME
BEFORE HE O.D.'s ANYWAY.

27:16.235 --> 27:17.707
MIGHT AS WELL
HELP HIM ALONG."

27:17.707 --> 27:19.709
I DIDN'T --
IT'S OVER.

27:19.709 --> 27:21.410
YOU'LL FACE A MILITARY
TRIBUNAL FOR THE FRIENDLY
FIRE AND THE COVER-UP --

27:21.410 --> 27:23.943
PROBABLY SPEND THE REST
OF YOUR LIFE IN LEAVENWORTH.

27:23.943 --> 27:26.045
TWO MORE MURDERS
DON'T MAKE A DIFFERENCE.

27:28.147 --> 27:29.648
TELL US WHAT HAPPENED.

27:31.921 --> 27:34.784
HICKS WAS ALREADY OUT OF IT
WHEN I GOT THERE.

27:49.769 --> 27:53.773
I GUESS I JUST CONVINCED MYSELF
HE'D BE BETTER OFF DEAD.

27:55.975 --> 28:01.150
I MEAN, HIS LIFE HAD ALREADY
BECOME SUCH A WASTE.

28:01.150 --> 28:03.152
AND THAT
MAKES KILLING HIM OKAY?

28:03.152 --> 28:06.155
SURE, IT HAD TO BE DONE.
YOU NEEDED A FALL GUY.

28:06.155 --> 28:08.017
YOU'D ALREADY KILLED
LARRY McPHEE.

28:08.017 --> 28:10.419
HE TOLD HICKS HE WAS GONNA
BLOW THE WHISTLE ON THE RAPE.

28:10.419 --> 28:11.821
HICKS OBVIOUSLY TOLD YOU,

28:11.821 --> 28:13.923
AND YOU KNEW
IT WAS ALL GONNA COME OUT --

28:13.923 --> 28:15.795
THE FRIENDLY FIRE,
THE COVER-UP.

28:15.795 --> 28:18.097
YOU HAD TO STOP HIM
BEFORE HE WENT TO KENDRA.

28:18.097 --> 28:19.969
NO, I JUST WENT THERE
TO TALK TO HIM.

28:19.969 --> 28:21.470
I GOT TO TELL HER
THE TRUTH, SIR.

28:21.470 --> 28:23.272
SHE DESERVES
BETTER THAN SHE GOT.

28:23.272 --> 28:24.904
McPHEE, DON'T DO THIS.

28:24.904 --> 28:26.305
HEY.

28:31.881 --> 28:34.784
Brock: I DIDN'T WANT TO DO IT.
HE WOULDN'T LISTEN.

28:37.416 --> 28:38.848
[ GRUNTS ]

28:44.723 --> 28:46.725
AND THEN YOU NOT ONLY
TAKE OUT HICKS,

28:46.725 --> 28:48.828
YOU FRAME HIM
FOR LARRY'S MURDER.

28:48.828 --> 28:50.229
IT WASN'T MY IDEA.

28:51.260 --> 28:54.363
RICKFORD SAID IF I DIDN'T
SHUT THEM UP, HE'D DESTROY ME.

28:54.363 --> 28:57.066
BLAKE RICKFORD
TOLD YOU TO KILL THEM?

28:57.066 --> 28:59.508
NOT BLAKE.

29:10.349 --> 29:14.053
WHAT THE HELL'S
GOING ON HERE?

29:14.053 --> 29:18.187
JUST GIVING YOU A LITTLE
HEADS-UP, CONGRESSMAN.

29:18.187 --> 29:20.429
BROCK ALECKSEN
JUST GAVE A SWORN STATEMENT

29:20.429 --> 29:23.232
TO THE U.S. ATTORNEY
SAYING THAT YOU BLACKMAILED HIM

29:23.232 --> 29:25.534
INTO KILLING LARRY McPHEE
AND ANTHONY HICKS.

29:25.534 --> 29:27.366
THAT'S RIDICULOUS.
Daniel: COME ON.

29:27.366 --> 29:29.538
W-WHEN BLAKE HEARD THAT McPHEE
WAS GONNA COME CLEAN,

29:29.538 --> 29:31.170
HE CAME RUNNING
STRAIGHT FOR DADDY,

29:31.170 --> 29:32.902
TOLD YOU ALL ABOUT
THE FRIENDLY FIRE.

29:32.902 --> 29:34.904
THEN YOU TOLD ALECKSEN
IF HE DIDN'T FIX THE PROBLEM,

29:34.904 --> 29:36.906
YOU'D RUIN HIM.
I NEVER TOLD HIM
TO KILL ANYBODY.

29:36.906 --> 29:39.078
WELL, YOU MIGHT NOT HAVE
USED THE WORD "MURDER,"

29:39.078 --> 29:41.380
BUT YOU'LL BE CHARGED
AS A CO-CONSPIRATOR.

29:41.380 --> 29:44.553
BASED ON THE DUBIOUS TESTIMONY
OF A CONFESSED KILLER?

29:44.553 --> 29:45.885
I DON'T THINK SO.

29:45.885 --> 29:47.987
I'M A UNITED STATES
CONGRESSMAN.

29:47.987 --> 29:49.819
EVEN IF THESE CHARGES
DON'T STICK,

29:49.819 --> 29:51.220
YOUR POLITICAL CAREER
IS OVER.

29:51.220 --> 29:52.561
PRESS WILL EAT YOU ALIVE.

29:52.561 --> 29:55.164
HEY, REMEMBER
WHAT YOU SAID TO ME IN COURT?

29:55.164 --> 29:58.197
WELL, IT TURNS OUT MY EX-WIFE
DIDN'T SCREW UP MY LIFE.

29:58.197 --> 30:00.900
BUT YOUR PRECIOUS SON
SURE SCREWED UP YOURS.

30:00.900 --> 30:02.471
MY SON WAS AN IDIOT.

30:02.471 --> 30:04.403
EVERY
CRAZY IDEA HE HAD,

30:04.403 --> 30:07.977
EVERY HAIR-BRAINED SCHEME
THAT HE TRIED, HE SCREWED UP.

30:07.977 --> 30:10.009
EXPELLED FROM
THREE PREP SCHOOLS,

30:10.009 --> 30:12.341
FIRED FROM COUNTLESS JOBS,
HOOKERS, STRIP CLUBS.

30:12.341 --> 30:14.513
HE COULDN'T EVEN KEEP HIS HANDS
OFF THE LADIES

30:14.513 --> 30:17.446
WHEN HE KNEW THAT THE FBI
WAS FOLLOWING HIM.

30:17.446 --> 30:19.889
I FORCED HIM TO ENLIST.

30:19.889 --> 30:21.520
THOUGHT MAYBE
MILITARY DISCIPLINE

30:21.520 --> 30:23.422
WOULD STRAIGHTEN
HIS SORRY ASS OUT,

30:23.422 --> 30:27.296
BUT DEEP DOWN...
I HOPED HE'D COME HOME IN A BOX.

30:27.296 --> 30:29.458
AND WHEN HE FINALLY
GOT HIMSELF KILLED,

30:29.458 --> 30:30.930
I WASN'T SAD.

30:30.930 --> 30:32.331
I WAS RELIEVED.

30:32.331 --> 30:34.133
DONE WITH CLEANING UP
HIS MESSES.

30:34.133 --> 30:36.866
I'M NOT GOING DOWN
FOR HIS MISTAKES.

30:36.866 --> 30:39.308
NOW GET THE HELL OUT
OF MY OFFICE.

30:41.540 --> 30:44.413
Donnie:
THE C.O. WILL TESTIFY FOR YOU.

30:44.413 --> 30:47.446
WE CAN FINALLY PROVE THAT
BLAKE RICKFORD RAPED KENDRA.

30:47.446 --> 30:49.178
IT'S TOO LATE.

30:49.178 --> 30:51.280
IF I TAKE THIS TO TRIAL,
THE PROSECUTOR WILL DESTROY ME.

30:51.280 --> 30:53.422
THEY'LL JUST SAY THAT
I WAS OBSESSED WITH RICKFORD.

30:53.422 --> 30:55.384
THAT'S THEIR SIDE OF THE STORY.
YOU HAVE TO TELL YOURS.

30:55.384 --> 30:57.126
WHAT'S TO TELL?

30:57.126 --> 30:59.388
I THOUGHT THAT HE WAS RAPING
A WOMAN, BUT HE WASN'T.

30:59.388 --> 31:00.990
HE WASN'T A MURDERER,
EITHER.

31:02.561 --> 31:05.564
AND I WAS WRONG, AND I HAVE TO
PAY FOR WHAT I DID.

31:07.096 --> 31:09.468
KATE --
CALL ERLICH.
TELL HIM I'LL TAKE THE DEAL.

31:09.468 --> 31:12.401
NO.
WE'RE GONNA FIGHT THIS.

31:12.401 --> 31:13.572
DONNIE, MAKE THE CALL.

31:25.114 --> 31:27.256
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]
LEWICKI!

31:27.256 --> 31:29.018
[ KNOCKING CONTINUES ]

31:29.018 --> 31:31.160
LEWICK--
[ SIGHS ]

31:37.166 --> 31:39.168
MIRANDA,
IT'S NOT A GOOD TIME.

31:39.168 --> 31:41.170
I WANT TO MEET HER.

31:41.170 --> 31:42.331
WHO?

31:42.331 --> 31:43.432
NATALIE.

31:43.432 --> 31:45.304
I TOLD YOU
SHE'S NOT REAL.

31:45.304 --> 31:47.506
WELL,
SHE'S REAL TO YOU.

31:47.506 --> 31:49.038
WHAT? ARE YOU AFRAID
I WON'T LIKE HER?

31:49.038 --> 31:50.909
OR THAT SHE WON'T LIKE ME?
NO --

31:50.909 --> 31:52.511
OF COURSE
SHE'D LIKE YOU.

31:52.511 --> 31:54.383
THEN INTRODUCE ME.
IT DOESN'T WORK LIKE THAT.

31:54.383 --> 31:56.545
I-I-I CAN'T
JUST SUMMON HER.

31:56.545 --> 31:59.188
WHAT'S WITH YOU
AND THESE LOOPY BROADS?

32:01.550 --> 32:05.554
SHE WANTS TO MEET
YOUR IMAGINARY GIRLFRIEND.

32:05.554 --> 32:08.958
TALK ABOUT
A HAIR-BRAINED SCHEME.

32:08.958 --> 32:10.960
HAIR-BRAINED SCHEME...

32:10.960 --> 32:13.002
IS SHE TALKING TO YOU
RIGHT NOW?

32:13.002 --> 32:14.203
NO.

32:16.465 --> 32:18.037
LIKE HIS DADDY SAID,

32:18.037 --> 32:20.669
THAT BOY RICKFORD
SURE HAD A LOT OF BAD IDEAS,

32:20.669 --> 32:23.472
BUT PICKING UP THAT GIRL
WHEN HE KNEW THAT

32:23.472 --> 32:26.615
THAT LITTLE PISTOL KATE MORETTI
WAS FOLLOWING HIM,

32:26.615 --> 32:29.218
THAT WAS
THE MOST HAIR-BRAINED OF ALL.

32:29.218 --> 32:31.380
DANIEL.
COULD I GET
A RIDE DOWNTOWN?

32:33.022 --> 32:34.653
MS. MORETTI.

32:34.653 --> 32:37.286
IT IS MY UNDERSTANDING THAT
YOU WISH TO CHANGE YOUR PLEA?

32:37.286 --> 32:40.159
YES, YOUR HONOR.
STOP! I'M S-SORRY,
YOUR HONOR.

32:40.159 --> 32:41.991
KATE, DON'T DO THIS.

32:41.991 --> 32:44.263
DANIEL, PLEASE.
YOUR PERCEPTION WAS WRONG
THAT NIGHT.

32:44.263 --> 32:46.135
BLAKE RICKFORD
WAS NOT GONNA COMMIT A RAPE.

32:46.135 --> 32:49.068
YES, I KNOW.
THAT'S WHY I'M STANDING HERE.

32:49.068 --> 32:51.140
HE WAS GONNA COMMIT
A MURDER.
WHOSE?

32:51.140 --> 32:52.401
YOURS.

32:57.076 --> 32:58.277
THE CONGRESSMAN SAID

32:58.277 --> 32:59.648
HIS SON COULDN'T
KEEP HIS HANDS OFF WOMEN

32:59.648 --> 33:02.351
EVEN THOUGH HE KNEW
THE FBI WAS FOLLOWING HIM.

33:02.351 --> 33:04.053
HE MADE YOU, KATE.

33:04.053 --> 33:05.714
I DON'T KNOW, DANIEL.
I'M PRETTY GOOD AT SURVEILLANCE.

33:05.714 --> 33:07.156
WELL,
YOU DID TELL RICKFORD

33:07.156 --> 33:09.488
YOU'D BE WATCHING
HIS EVERY MOVE.

33:09.488 --> 33:12.021
OKAY, SAY IT'S POSSIBLE.
WHAT DIFFERENCE DOES IT MAKE?

33:12.021 --> 33:13.592
THAT'S THE WRONG QUESTION.
WRONG QUESTION.

33:13.592 --> 33:15.764
THE RIGHT QUESTION IS
WHY WOULD RICKFORD RAPE A WOMAN

33:15.764 --> 33:17.626
IF HE KNEW
YOU WERE WATCHING HIM?

33:17.626 --> 33:20.329
HE WOULDN'T.
EXACTLY. EXACTLY.

33:20.329 --> 33:23.202
HE -- THE WHOLE THING WAS AN ACT
TO LURE YOU IN AND KILL YOU.

33:23.202 --> 33:25.204
I DON'T KNOW, DANIEL.
IT SOUNDS PRETTY NUTS.

33:25.204 --> 33:26.705
WELL, THE --
THE CONGRESSMAN ALSO SAID

33:26.705 --> 33:28.237
THAT -- THAT BLAKE
WAS CONSTANTLY COMING UP

33:28.237 --> 33:29.408
WITH HAIR-BRAINED SCHEMES.

33:29.408 --> 33:30.609
THAT MAKES SENSE.

33:30.609 --> 33:32.481
YOU SWORE
TO MAKE HIS LIFE HELL.

33:32.481 --> 33:34.483
HE KNEW YOU'D PROVE THE RAPE
NO MATTER HOW LONG IT TOOK,

33:34.483 --> 33:36.185
SO HE HAD TO TRY
AND GET RID OF YOU.

33:36.185 --> 33:39.688
OKAY, SAY YOU'RE RIGHT.
HOW DO WE PROVE IT?

33:43.092 --> 33:44.753
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

33:46.755 --> 33:50.629
YOU MUST BE DONNIE.
I'M CANDY.

33:50.629 --> 33:53.262
I THINK I'VE GOT
A CAVITY ALREADY.

33:53.262 --> 33:54.533
[ CHUCKLES ]

33:54.533 --> 33:55.564
PLEASE, COME IN.

34:02.671 --> 34:07.216
$5,000.

34:07.216 --> 34:11.720
DON'T WORRY, BABY.
I'M WORTH EVERY PENNY.

34:14.083 --> 34:15.654
[ SIGHS ]

34:15.654 --> 34:20.659
SINCE THIS IS OUR FIRST TIME,
I'D LIKE TO KNOW WHAT YOU LIKE.

34:20.659 --> 34:24.062
ACTUALLY,
I JUST WANT TO TALK.

34:25.564 --> 34:26.665
WENDY.

34:26.665 --> 34:28.837
[ CHUCKLES ]

34:28.837 --> 34:31.340
THAT'S NOT MY NAME.
SURE, IT IS.

34:31.340 --> 34:33.772
I WATCHED YOU GIVE A SWORN
STATEMENT TO THE U.S. ATTORNEY

34:33.772 --> 34:35.574
ABOUT THE NIGHT
BLAKE RICKFORD DIED.

34:35.574 --> 34:38.147
I'M REPRESENTING THE WOMAN
ACCUSED OF KILLING HIM.

34:38.147 --> 34:39.348
I'M OUT OF HERE.

34:39.348 --> 34:40.649
I HAD YOU FOLLOWED.

34:42.381 --> 34:43.682
YOU HAVE
QUITE A SOCIAL LIFE.

34:43.682 --> 34:46.755
ON TUESDAY,
YOU WERE WITH ALDERMAN LOMAX.

34:46.755 --> 34:49.788
I ASKED HIM ABOUT YOU,
AND SINCE HE REALLY WANTED

34:49.788 --> 34:52.591
HIS LIAISONS WITH A CALL GIRL
KEPT PRIVATE,

34:52.591 --> 34:54.763
HE GAVE UP
YOUR SUPER-SECRET PHONE NUMBER,

34:54.763 --> 34:57.766
WHICH I'M TOLD
IS VERY HARD TO COME BY.

34:59.468 --> 35:04.102
YOU PAID TAXES ON 60K A YEAR
FROM YOUR PHONY DECORATING JOB,

35:04.102 --> 35:07.676
BUT I'M BETTING THE REAL MONEY
IS UNDER A SWISS MATTRESS

35:07.676 --> 35:09.238
OR IN THE CAYMANS.

35:09.238 --> 35:12.341
THE GOVERNMENT
WILL TAKE IT ALL -- EVERY PENNY.

35:12.341 --> 35:15.314
BUT IF YOU HELP ME,

35:15.314 --> 35:19.188
I'LL TALK TO THE U.S. ATTORNEY
ABOUT GETTING YOU IMMUNITY.

35:26.555 --> 35:29.598
BLAKE RICKFORD HIRED ME TO
MEET HIM AT THE BAR THAT NIGHT.

35:29.598 --> 35:35.404
HE SAID HE LIKED TIPSY WOMEN,
SO I PRETENDED I WAS DRUNK.

35:38.267 --> 35:40.138
HE WAS A LITTLE ROUGH,

35:40.138 --> 35:42.441
BUT I JUST THOUGHT
THAT WAS A PART OF HIS ACT.

35:42.441 --> 35:45.214
IN THE CAR, HE KEPT ON LOOKING
IN THE REARVIEW MIRROR,

35:45.214 --> 35:47.546
BUT AT HIS PLACE,

35:47.546 --> 35:50.749
HE INSISTED THAT WE MAKE OUT
IN FRONT OF HIS WINDOW,

35:50.749 --> 35:53.922
LIKE HE WANTED
SOMEONE TO SEE US.

35:53.922 --> 35:55.624
HE TOLD ME TO SCREAM...

35:55.624 --> 35:57.526
[ SCREAMS ]
...SO I DID.

36:03.532 --> 36:05.264
I THOUGHT
IT WAS JUST A GAME.

36:05.264 --> 36:06.835
[ GLASS SHATTERS ]

36:06.835 --> 36:08.697
BUT WHEN WE HEARD SOMEONE
BREAKING IN,

36:08.697 --> 36:10.239
HE DIDN'T SEEM WORRIED,

36:10.239 --> 36:13.472
LIKE HE KNEW
WHAT WAS GONNA HAPPEN.

36:13.472 --> 36:15.604
HE SOUNDED AFRAID,
BUT HE WAS CALM.

36:15.604 --> 36:17.306
THERE'S A CRAZY WOMAN
STALKING ME.

36:17.306 --> 36:19.408
SHE JUST BROKE INTO MY HOUSE.
PLEASE SEND HELP.

36:19.408 --> 36:21.480
I-I THINK SHE'S GOT A GUN.
SHE'S GONNA KILL ME.

36:22.881 --> 36:27.356
HE GRABBED HIS GUN RIGHT THERE,
LIKE HE WAS READY FOR IT.

36:27.356 --> 36:30.188
I DIDN'T KNOW
WHAT WAS GOING DOWN,

36:30.188 --> 36:33.522
BUT I JUST KNEW
I DIDN'T WANT ANY PART OF IT.

36:34.463 --> 36:36.965
SO I GOT
THE HELL OUT OF THERE.

36:36.965 --> 36:39.528
Donnie:
UNTIL THE NEXT DAY,

36:39.528 --> 36:41.700
WHEN IT WAS ALL OVER THE NEWS
THAT AN FBI AGENT

36:41.700 --> 36:43.702
HAD GUNNED DOWN
A CONGRESSMAN'S SON.

36:43.702 --> 36:45.804
YOU SAW DOLLAR SIGNS.

36:45.804 --> 36:47.836
I WENT AND SAW
THE CONGRESSMAN.

36:47.836 --> 36:49.908
HE GAVE ME 200 GRAND

36:49.908 --> 36:51.610
TO TELL THE FBI
A FAIRY TALE

36:51.610 --> 36:55.614
ABOUT MY PERFECT DATE
WITH HIS PERFECT SON.

36:55.614 --> 36:58.317
AND THEY BOUGHT IT.

36:58.317 --> 37:00.319
CANNOT BELIEVE
SHE SNOWED US.

37:00.319 --> 37:04.323
WELL,
SHE'S VERY PERSUASIVE.

37:04.323 --> 37:07.826
NOW, ABOUT
THAT MURDER CHARGE.

37:07.826 --> 37:09.258
Judge Cabrera:
CASE DISMISSED.

37:09.258 --> 37:10.959
AGENT MORETTI,
YOU'RE FREE TO GO.

37:14.863 --> 37:16.234
DANIEL.

37:17.706 --> 37:20.539
YOU NEVER STOPPED
BELIEVING IN ME.

37:20.539 --> 37:23.342
JUST
RETURNING THE FAVOR.

37:28.977 --> 37:31.520
IT WAS A HELL OF A JOB...

37:31.520 --> 37:34.683
FOR A PINKO LIBERAL
COLLEGE PROFESSOR.

37:34.683 --> 37:37.686
THANK YOU
FOR YOUR SERVICE.

37:46.495 --> 37:48.997
I'M CERTIFYING YOU
FIT FOR DUTY.

37:48.997 --> 37:51.700
NO MORE THERAPY
REQUIRED.

37:51.700 --> 37:53.572
THANK YOU.

37:53.572 --> 37:55.444
GOODBYE, KATE.

37:58.877 --> 38:01.510
SO, I'LL SEE YOU
NEXT WEEK?

38:01.510 --> 38:03.352
MONDAY AT 10:00.

38:08.857 --> 38:12.561
IT'S KIND OF LIKE
A SéANCE.

38:12.561 --> 38:15.424
IT'S A LITTLE AWKWARD.

38:17.466 --> 38:19.698
IS SHE HERE?

38:19.698 --> 38:20.799
YEP. YEP.

38:20.799 --> 38:23.472
DON'T WORRY.
I'M OKAY WITH IT.

38:24.703 --> 38:29.708
I'M GONNA GIVE YOU TWO
SOME PRIVACY.

38:29.708 --> 38:31.810
WELL, IS...

38:31.810 --> 38:33.311
SHE'S GONE.

38:42.050 --> 38:45.754
HEY.

38:45.754 --> 38:48.096
THOUGHT YOU MIGHT BE IN THE MOOD
FOR SOME HOP LI.

38:48.096 --> 38:50.058
BROUGHT YOU
SOME EGG ROLLS.

38:50.058 --> 38:51.600
LOOKS LIKE ENOUGH
TO FEED AN ARMY.

38:51.600 --> 38:53.602
DO YOU WANT TO JOIN ME?

38:53.602 --> 38:55.504
NAH,
I GOT TO BE UP EARLY.

38:55.504 --> 38:57.666
BUT YOU'VE EXONERATED
YOUR ONE AND ONLY CLIENT.

38:57.666 --> 38:59.738
WHAT ARE YOU GONNA DO NOW?
CHASE AMBULANCES?

38:59.738 --> 39:00.869
[ CHUCKLES ]

39:00.869 --> 39:02.871
ACTUALLY,
I GOT MY OLD JOB BACK.

39:02.871 --> 39:05.113
AND I GOT A BONUS.

39:05.113 --> 39:06.875
I'M PROSECUTING
CONGRESSMAN RICKFORD.

39:08.917 --> 39:09.918
THAT'S BETTER
THAN A RAISE.

39:16.685 --> 39:18.086
DO YOU WANT TO KNOW
WHAT THE WORST PART

39:18.086 --> 39:19.828
OF THIS WHOLE THING WAS?

39:19.828 --> 39:25.894
WAS REALIZING THAT I HAVE
NO LIFE OUTSIDE OF MY JOB.

39:29.037 --> 39:31.970
I GOT TO FIX THAT.

39:53.061 --> 39:54.392
I SHOULD GO.

39:54.392 --> 39:57.826
BUT YOU COULD STAY.

39:57.826 --> 40:00.729
KATE.

40:00.729 --> 40:04.933
I WANT TO STAY
MORE THAN ANYTHING IN THE WORLD.

40:07.706 --> 40:10.408
BUT I SCREWED US UP ONCE.

40:10.408 --> 40:14.012
AND IF YOU GIVE ME
ANOTHER CHANCE,

40:14.012 --> 40:16.715
I'M GONNA DO IT RIGHT
THIS TIME.

40:16.715 --> 40:20.048
BUT DONNIE, IT'S OKAY.

40:20.048 --> 40:22.491
YOU'VE BEEN THROUGH
A LOT AND --

40:22.491 --> 40:26.154
AND YOU'RE FEELING
VULNERABLE.

40:26.154 --> 40:29.027
SO, AS MUCH AS I WANT TO SWEEP
YOU OFF YOUR FEET RIGHT NOW

40:29.027 --> 40:30.959
AND CARRY YOU
INTO THAT BEDROOM...

40:33.201 --> 40:35.033
...I'M GONNA LEAVE.

40:52.551 --> 40:56.054
"THERE ARE NO SECOND ACTS
IN AMERICAN LIVES."

40:56.054 --> 40:57.656
WHO SAID IT?

40:57.656 --> 40:59.528
FITZGERALD.
YES.

40:59.528 --> 41:02.991
BUT F. SCOTT SHOULD HAVE
BRUSHED UP ON HIS NEUROSCIENCE,

41:02.991 --> 41:07.636
BECAUSE THERE CAN BE
A SECOND ACT FOR THE BRAIN.

41:07.636 --> 41:11.139
DEVASTATED BY INJURY,
THE BRAINS OF ORDINARY PEOPLE

41:11.139 --> 41:13.772
CAN DEVELOP
AMAZING NEW SKILLS --

41:13.772 --> 41:15.674
A SECOND ACT, IF YOU WILL,

41:15.674 --> 41:19.548
KNOWN AS
ACQUIRED SAVANT SYNDROME.

41:19.548 --> 41:22.551
A HIGH-SCHOOL DROPOUT
IS SAVAGELY ATTACKED.

41:22.551 --> 41:24.553
HE AWAKENS ABLE TO DRAW

41:24.553 --> 41:28.486
MATHEMATICALLY ACCURATE
FRACTALS BY HAND.

41:28.486 --> 41:32.220
AFTER A STROKE, A DOCTOR
WITH NO PREVIOUS INTEREST IN ART

41:32.220 --> 41:34.022
BECOMES A GIFTED PAINTER.

41:34.022 --> 41:37.626
HIS WORK ADORNS GALLERY WALLS
AND MAGAZINE PAGES.

41:37.626 --> 41:40.999
SO, IF OUR BRAINS CAN HAVE
A SECOND ACT,

41:40.999 --> 41:43.101
WHY NOT OUR LIVES?

41:46.705 --> 41:50.208
BROKEN LIVES CAN BE HEALED.

41:53.281 --> 41:56.184
JUSTICE CAN FINALLY PREVAIL.

42:00.919 --> 42:03.191
DAMAGED RELATIONSHIPS REPAIRED.

42:05.794 --> 42:08.126
SINS CAN BE FORGIVEN.

42:11.529 --> 42:15.033
AND WRONGS CAN BE RIGHTED.

42:16.965 --> 42:23.311
IN OUR LIVES, AS IN OUR BRAINS,
WE ALL DESERVE A SECOND CHANCE.

42:28.577 --> 42:31.580
WE JUST HAVE TO BE
BRAVE ENOUGH TO SEE.
